 \text{Probability} = \sum_{i=m}^{n} \frac{\prod^{i}_{n - i + 1}}{m!} \cdot \left(\frac{n-i+1}{n}\right)^i \cdot \left(\frac{n-i-1}{n}\right)^{n-i} 
